description: Taquero Fusion has taken flavors from Latin American Countries and created a Taco Twist menu that made its debut on the first Taquero Fusion taco truck in Chicago, June 2011.  Taquero Fusion's on-site taco grill catering can make your next corporate and private event a hit.We are the next up and coming gourmet taco catering company providing excellent service in the Chicago Land area and surrounding suburbs. We specialize in Tacos with a Latin twist.
name: Taquero Fusion
